{
  "stem": "3360.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I think the law had already been passed that you weren't supposed to go into the movie theaters.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we sat there and loudly laughed like idiots, but like-- like young teenagers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Nobody bothered us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the years there I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I really didn't care much for any of the teachers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There were-- there was an occasional absence of this one or that one at which time, this Dr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Jonas, who was the father, who was the principal, would then take over a class and teach a class.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I thought he was a marvelous teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So I enjoyed that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I don't know what very much else I enjoyed there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The last year, I had-- I did have a teacher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I was in another location, which had formally been a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a single family home, and then a Jewish school, a Jewish private school, a private Jewish girl's school.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they took that over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And so the older-- some of the older students would attend there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And that's where I was going in 1938.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And when the-- when it happened that-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a young Polish Jew had shot and killed a second or third rate-- not a second or third rate-- but a minor-- a minor official in the German embassy in Paris.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And, oh, outrage.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Outrage in the press.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "This was not amongst Germans as such, but outrage in the press.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "How dare a Jew kill a German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And this is what then brought on what is-- what later became to-- came to be known as Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "The outrage over this act by this young Polish Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And what happened had happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
